f) File patent applications based on the Framework

4. INTEGRATION DEVELOPMENT

Licensee may:
a) Develop custom integrations within licensed quotas
b) Use development and testing environments with proper licensing
c) Deploy integrations within Licensee's organization

Integration development must:
a) Maintain all security controls and requirements
b) Comply with documentation and usage guidelines
c) Pass automated compliance verification

5. USAGE REQUIREMENTS

Licensee must:
a) Maintain valid license keys and API access credentials
